            . On the 9th of October, I employed the prisoner to take a box to the coach office - it was not quite ready when he came, and I told him to wait in the kitchen. I missed two tea spoons off the tea tray, in the kitchen, soon after he was gone.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18231022-26-person290">
                  ISAAC 
                  LYONS
               <interp inst="t18231022-26-person290" type="surname" value="LYONS"></interp>
