                     <interp inst="t18231022-26-person290" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a jeweller, and live in High-street, St. Giles's. A boy brought two spoons into my shop, and offered them for sale - on my questioning him, he pointed to the prisoner, as having sent him with them. I asked him where he got them - he said a man at the corner of Oxford-street gave them him to sell.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I did take them.</p>
